{"tid":1979141,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【星二代】自小虎媽利智嚴格教育入讀全美頂尖學府　李連杰細女留家抗疫致抑鬱復發","createTime":"2020-04-19T08:14:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T10:24:56.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"64965b195302b7bc30ced4dc060888f50cdf8b02","tid":1979141,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎肆虐全球，市民們都會選擇留家抗疫，減少外出，而李連杰16歲的細女Jada正於美國著名學府Phillips Academy升讀高中，而美國的疫情亦很嚴峻，Jada亦無可避免留家抗疫，而她昨日於IG透露在家隔離期間導致抑鬱症復發，幸好獲專業人士幫助。<br />\n<br />\n李連杰16歲的細女Jada昨日於Instagram貼出個人照，兼配文道：「隔離確實對我的心理健康造成了傷害。我曾經有焦慮和重度抑鬱症的病歷，目前正經歷著非常嚴重的復發，我以為過唔到呢一關，很幸運能夠獲得專業人士幫助。」<br />\n<br />\n她之後更鼓勵大眾，若因隔離而導致焦慮症不用害怕，她寫道：「我想在這裡跟大家說，如果你遇到類似情況，你並不孤單，好多人都因為要隔離產生焦慮，只要你上網，當中有好多危機熱線或者網站可以幫到你忙，如果你沒有這種情況，請留意你的親人與身邊朋友，並確保佢哋一切正常，因為冇人想獨自經歷這情況。」 <br />\n<br />\n現年16歲的Jada跟胞姊Jane自小在新加坡長大，在當地接受中西方教育，學好中文，新加坡的教育亦出名嚴謹。而媽媽利智亦對女兒的教育非常嚴格。<br />\n<br />\n李連杰更形容她為「非常虎媽」，在大女9個月大時就聘請老師，後來她竟說「教晚了」，在細女未夠6個月大就請老師。李連杰曾解釋：「6個月大的孩子已可以吸收色彩及聲音，你在搖鈴她就會搖頭。」<br />\n<br />\n而Jada甚具音樂天份，11歲時已在新加坡作長笛表演，於新加坡完成學業後，Jada跟隨胞姐Jane到美國留學，現就讀美國最著名兼最早開辦的私立寄宿學校Phillips Academy。<br />\n<br />\n1778年創校的Phillips Academy，歷年來孕育出大批傑出人才，包括前美國總統約翰甘迺迪、喬治布殊父子及摩斯電碼發明者薩繆爾摩斯（Samuel Morse）等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2621341/lee_thumb_20200418_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2621341%2Flee_thumb_20200418_ch_1024.jpg&h=e17276a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2621341/_jadali_9_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2621341%2F_jadali_9_1024.jpg&h=df76407d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2621341/_jadali_78713265_163474904718433_1655187491971210771_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2621341%2F_jadali_78713265_163474904718433_1655187491971210771_n_1024.jpg&h=aa5e5e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2620000/2621341/_jadali_69348581_221268378861331_5254175155305808168_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2620000%2F2621341%2F_jadali_69348581_221268378861331_5254175155305808168_n_1024.jpg&h=ff6d567e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6cbc01bf5dcf5ad81acbf146ea32dd3efbe9790","tid":1979141,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:22:16.000Z","msg":"應該未來會嫁鬼仔"},{"pid":"72bc61da1fb41b549188def6db4d337bb452b367","tid":1979141,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7166f2773342f25efd81a6779588e87b1017c5a9","tid":1979141,"uid":244759,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"口講愛國，身在美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"eb02a35ebb9c1519973beb48b347cad8fe2d0e7b","tid":1979141,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T08:31:07.000Z","msg":"利智<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155efb75b9d873d50c6893652c5e057907a50c52","tid":1979141,"uid":41352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep